virtusa  wikipedia virtusa from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search virtusa corporation type public traded as nasdaq vrtu sp  component industry information technology services founded  massachusetts united states founder kris canekeratne tushara canekeratne john gillis sandy gillis headquarters westborough massachusetts united states area served united states united kingdom germany the netherlands hungary india singapore and sri lanka services consulting business consulting application development product development legacy asset management revenue   million fy net income   million fy number of employees    website wwwvirtusacom virtusa corporation nasdaq vrtu is a global information technology services company founded in  with its headquarters in westborough massachusetts united states the company provides it consulting business consulting systems implementation and application outsourcing services to large enterprises and software vendors the company founded in  has delivery centers in the united states the united kingdom singapore germany malaysia the netherlands india and sri lanka contents  acquisitions  operations  competition  community support  offices  references  external links acquisitionsedit in  acquired insource a technology consulting company which specialized in insurance and healthcare industries insource is based in hartford connecticut us in  virtusa acquired convista consulting llc a usbased privately held market leader in finance transformation specifically focusing on high volume collection disbursement claims and billing systems in bfsi in the following year in  virtusa acquired alas consulting llc a financial services consulting firm in november  virtusa acquired osb consulting llc a new jerseybased consulting firm specializing in the financial services and insurance domains including sap finance capabilities at the start of  virtusa announced that it has acquired all the outstanding shares of tradetech consulting scandinavia ab and its subsidiaries tradetech headquartered in stockholm sweden is a consulting and it services provider specializing in treasury and asset management for major financial institutions in the nordic countries in  virtusa acquired all the outstanding shares of apparatus inc an it infrastructure services provider headquartered in indianapolis indiana in november  virtusa acquired a  stake in polaris consulting  services limited india an indian provider of it solutions primarily to banking and financial services virtusa paid  million for the firm which will see more than  employees join its global undertakings virtusa at orion city sri lanka operationsedit on  december  virtusa had  clients across the world with  employees locations virtusa has a global presence with offices throughout us europe and asia and advanced development centers in the united states europe and asia competitionedit some of its key competitors in the offshore it services industry include infosys wipro cognizant mphasis hcl and tata consultancy services among other organizations community supportedit the company has a community support program that focuses on education and uses its it competencies for meeting the needs of the community a team from virtusa designed and developed a school management system akura to assist schools with an effective mechanism to manage daily activities involved in running a school the school management system allows easy and centralised access to student information such as their schedule report cards attendance grades extracurricular activities etc as well as teacher information such as experience schedules etc through the system teachers and parents can collaboratively view students’ progress the system has been adopted by schools and universities from across different countries and downloaded more than  times virtusa facilitated setting up it laboratories for fifty schools in the uva province of sri lanka the program was carried out in partnership with a local university in sri lanka earlier in  the company leveraged its technologyqa expertise to support the one laptop per child olpc program in the wake of tsunami in  its employees actively participated in the development of sahana an open source based disaster management officesedit united states  westborough massachusetts corporate headquarters indianapolis in new york new york windsor connecticut united kingdom  london germany  munich austria  austria switzerland  zurich the netherlands  amsterdam the hague sweden  stockholm gothenburg hungary  budapest india  hyderabad chennai bangalore mumbai pune gurgaon sri lanka  colombo singapore  singapore malaysia  kuala lumpur philippines  taguig city referencesedit  a b httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsvirtusaannouncesfourthquarterfullhtml  virtusapolaris in tune to achieve target of synergy revenue of  mn   virtusa acquires insource   marino jonathan httpwwwthemiddlemarketcomnewsvirtusacompletesconvistabuyhtml  missing or empty title help  httpwwwthemiddlemarketcomnewsvirtusacompletesconvistabuyhtml  missing or empty title help  httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsvirtusaexpandsinfrastructuremanagementserviceshtml  missing or empty title help  httpwwwconsultancyuknewsitgiantvirtusabuyspolarisconsultingandservices  missing or empty title help  investor sheet integrated corporate relations icr retrieved  apr    worldwide locations virtusacom retrieved  apr    httpwwwsundaytimeslkbusinesstimesbthtml  missing or empty title help  httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsvirtusawinswitsaglobalhtml  missing or empty title help  virtusa supports  rural schools – press releases on the sunday times    virtusa supports one laptop per child program – press releases on csrwirecom  external linksedit virtusa google finance profile qa with krishan a canekeratne ceo virtusa corp retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlevirtusaoldid categories companies established in software companies of sri lankasoftware companies based in massachusettsinternational information 