ess the system has been adopted by schools and universities from across different countries and downloaded more than  times virtusa facilitated setting up it laboratories for fifty schools in the uva province of sri lanka the program was carried out in partnership with a local university in sri lanka earlier in  the company leveraged its technologyqa expertise to support the one laptop per child olpc program in the wake of tsunami in  its employees actively participated in the development of sahana an open source based disaster management officesedit united states  westborough massachusetts corporate headquarters indianapolis in new york new york windsor connecticut united kingdom  london germany  munich austria  austria switzerland  zurich the netherlands  amsterdam the hague sweden  stockholm gothenburg hungary  budapest india  hyderabad chennai bangalore mumbai pune gurgaon sri lanka  colombo singapore  singapore malaysia  kuala lumpur philippines  taguig city referencesedit  a b httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsvirtusaannouncesfourthquarterfullhtml  virtusapolaris in tune to achieve target of synergy revenue of  mn   virtusa acquires insource   marino jonathan httpwwwthemiddlemarketcomnewsvirtusacompletesconvistabuyhtml  missing or empty title help  httpwwwthemiddlemarketcomnewsvirtusacompletesconvistabuyhtml  missing or empty title help  httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsvirtusaexpandsinfrastructuremanagementserviceshtml  missing or empty title help  httpwwwconsultancyuknewsitgiantvirtusabuyspolarisconsultingandservices  missing or empty title help  investor sheet integrated corporate relations icr retrieved  apr    worldwide locations virtusacom retrieved  apr    httpwwwsundaytimeslkbusinesstimesbthtml  missing or empty title help  httpsfinanceyahoocomnewsvirtusawinswitsaglobalhtml  missing or empty title help  virtusa supports  rural schools – press releases on the sunday times    virtusa supports one laptop per child program – press releases on csrwirecom  external linksedit v