ssues on the talk page learn how and when to remove these template messages this article has an unclear citation style the references used may be made clearer with a different or consistent style of citation footnoting or external linking january  learn how and when to remove this template message this article needs additional citations for verification please help improve this article by adding citations to reliable sources unsourced material may be challenged and removed november  learn how and when to remove this template message learn how and when to remove this template message polaris consulting  services limited type public traded as bse  nse polaris founded  headquarters chennai india area served worldwide key people kris canekeratne chairman services business consulting it services and business process outsourcing revenue us   million  profit us   million  number of employees    website wwwvirtusacom polaris consulting  services limited bse   nse polaris formerly polaris ft is a provider of financial technology products legacy modernization services and consulting for core banking corporate banking wealth  asset management and insurance  virtusa is the market facing brand of virtusa corporation and polaris consulting  services limited historyedit polaris has its origins in nucleus software polaris consulting  services limited was incorporated in  by mrravi dehariya jabalpur dist it was one of the first vendors that citi group chose to partner with when it entered india simultaneously citigroup started its own company called cosl citibank overseas software ltd to utilize the intellectual capital at a competitive cost in india cosl later renamed as orbitech was then merged with polaris in  polaris launched its core product portfolio intellecttm in november  the organization changed its name from polaris software labs limited to polaris financial technology limited to highlight its primary domain of operation on march   virtusa corporation acquired a majority stake in polaris consulting  services limited virtusapolaris is the market facing brand of virtusa corporation and polaris consulting  services limited  operations and global officesedit polaris is headquartered in chennai and has offices around the world in april  polaris launched its  ft design center  the worlds first center dedicated to financial technology  ft design center is spread over  sq ft and is located in the  acre polaris campus on the it highway in chennai milestonesedit  polaris software lab ltd incorporated   endtoend retail banking solution for citi bank india   quality processes aligned to sei cmm level    operations set up in usa  ullas trust – polaris’ csr was formed   first overseas development centre commissioned for citi bankcitation needed  wholly owned subsidiary founded in singapore and usacitation needed  polestar trust instituted to recognize excellence in business and it journalism   polaris awarded most innovative company  wholly owned subsidiary founded in uk   quality processes aligned to sei cmm level    quality processes iso  certified   birth of polaris retail infotech limited   initial public offering oversubscribed by  times   awarded best international business excellence award   became world’s first cmmi level  company   nasscom felicitated polaris software  ranked amongst top  best small companies in the world for the nd time   historic merger with orbitech citigroup subsidiary  birth of intellect   birth of optimus   the banker technology award   superspecialty center for financial risk management inaugurated in mumbai   launch of intellect suite of products for banking solutions   ranked th by nasscom top  exporters   received mother teresa corporate citizen award   world’s first super specialty center for investment banking the capital inaugurated in hyderabad   near shore centre inaugurated in belfast   entry into latin america   recognized as global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia   launched pace lab in sydney   won global leader in the specialty application development  nd year in a row   nearshore testing center inaugurated in canada   acquired seec inc the worldwide soa based insurance solution provider  polaris ullas trust won the best csr practice awards presented by bsenasscomtimes foundation  acquired laser soft info systems limited a leading banking software products company  laser soft won ndtv business leadership awards  under the ‘inclusion and diversity’ category  indigotx a saas company that provides go tx brokerage platform  launched intellect privacy internet banking security card an online and internet banking security card   launched intellect™ gub m  the most comprehensive enterprise banking solution   intellect wins the “early technology adopter” award at acord loma forum   polaris launches the school of financial technology   sampada a polarislaser soft initiative was awarded the best csr practice award at the th bse social and corporate governance awards jury meet held in mumbai  polaris makes strategic investment in identrust a global leader in trusted identity solutions  polaris was certified as ‘champion of learning’ by the american society of training and development astd  polaris wins two prestigious awards for its highly innovative core banking and wealth implementations at th asian banker technology implementation awards    polaris enters cloud computing space through strategic investment in identrust   entered into a business purchase agreement with pyxis a specialized player in front office and market risk related to cash and derivatives instruments subsidiariesedit apart from the polaris financial technology limited’s global subsidiaries the company has the following subsidiaries and associate companies polaris enterprise solutions limited pesl  a  subsidiary of polaris financial technology incorporated in india is a leading technology provider in retail manufacturing logistics  distribution telecom  media and travel industry nms works software private limited nms  nms is primarily engaged in the business of designing network management in telecommunication and internet services sonali polaris ft limited  polaris ft has entered into a jv agreement with sonali bank to implement online real time core banking solution for sonali bank and bangladesh commerce bank and offer services to other banks and financial institutions in bangladesh accordingly the company has incorporated a subsidiary company with  holding named sonali polaris ft limited in terms of the jv agreement education and trainingedit nalanda the corporate university of polaris is aimed at bringing the core of organizational processes together through learning and development initiatives that would enable associates to reach out to the latest modules and approaches to organizational learning polaris school of financial technology soft aims creating skilled associates to service its premier clients it will offer certificate courses at both the ‘primer’ and ‘practitioner’ levels executive fasttrack modules in retail banking core banking investment banking and corporate banking as well as customized enterprise training workshops the facility is located in hyderabad recognitionedit  polaris featured in fintech top  companies worldwide providing services to the financial sector at a rank of worldwide  polaris ullas trust wins the best csr practice awards presented by bsenasscomtimes foundation –   recognized as global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia  polaris intellect treasury won the banker capital markets projects award  rated amongst forbes world’s best small companies –  controversiesedit in december  the chairman of the company arun jain and sr vice president rajiv malhotra were detained by indonesian police over commercial dispute with a local bank artha graha on fraud charges jain and malhotra were released by the police after major diplomatic intervention by indian government in october  market regulator sebi barred polaris software labss cmd arun jain from securities market for a period of two years for insider trading in the companys shares sebi had charged him with trading in the stock on the basis of unpublished price sensitive information relating to a proposed acquisition by the firm sebi found that polaris software lab had called off the proposed acquisition of data inc after due diligence in the second week of september  but had informed the concerned stock exchanges on september   jain dealt in  shares of the company on behalf of polaris holding private ltd phpl on the basis of unpublished price sensitive information held by him and had made unfair gains to the tune of rs  lakh during the relevant time phpl was one of the promoters entity of polaris software labs and jain was one of the directors of phpl however in november  madras high court today stayed a sebi order which had barred polaris financial technology cmd arun jain from operating in securities market for a period of two years for alleged insider trading in the companys shares referencesedit  polaris consulting and services limited  head office   httpwwwmoneycontrolcomstocksstockmarketcorpnoticesphpautono  httpwwwmoneycontrolcomstocksstockmarketcorpnoticesphpautono  virtusapolaris in tune to achieve target of synergy revenue of  mn   httpwwwpolarisftcomaboutusaboutusasp  about aesys   financial technology ltd polaris company zxzxxzannouncements   citigroup partner   financial technology ltd polaris company announcements   httpeconomictimesindiatimescomtechitesvirtusapolarislaunchnewbrandidentityarticleshowcms  polaris launches ft   the worlds first design center for financial technology   polaris software lab ltd   citi bank   sei cmm level    ullas trust   polestar trust   wholly owned subsidiary founded in uk   sei cmm level    iso  certified   polaris retail infotech   initial public offering   best international business excellence   cmmi level    top  best small companies   merged with orbitech   intellect   optimus   the banker technology award   superspecialty center for financial risk management   intellect suite   ranked th by nasscom   mother teresa corporate citizen award   softwarelabltdtickerpolarissoftmajorsector super specialty center for investment banking check url value help   belfast   entry into latin america   global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia   pace lab   specialty application development  nd year in a row   nearshore testing center inaugurated in canada   polaris acquired seec   best csr practice awards   polaris acquired laser soft   laser soft won ndtv business leadership awards   polaris acquired indigotx   launched intellect privacy internet banking security card   launched intellect™ gub m    early technology adopter   polaris launches the school of financial technology   financialtechnologyltdtickerpolarisfinmajorsector sampada was awarded the best csr practice award check url value help   polaris invests in identrust   ‘champion of learning’   awards at th asian banker technology implementation awards    polaris enters cloud computing space   polaris acquired pyxis systems   solutions limited pesl polaris enterprise pesl   private limited nms works software nms   polaris ft limited sonali sonali polaris ft limited   corporate university of polaris nalanda nalanda   polaris school of financial technology polaris soft   polaris featured in fintech   polaris ullas trust wins the best csr practice awards   cybermedia   the banker capital markets projects award   world’s best small companies   ceo of indias polaris software is arrested by indonesian police   jakarta releases polaris cmd arun jain   sebi bars polaris arun jain from securities mkt for  years   hc stays sebi order restraining polaris chief from dealing in shares  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlevirtusapolarisoldid categories financial services companies of indiainformation technology companies of chennaih