  sampada a polarislaser soft initiative was awarded the best csr practice award at the th bse social and corporate governance awards jury meet held in mumbai  polaris makes strategic investment in identrust a global leader in trusted identity solutions  polaris was certified as ‘champion of learning’ by the american society of training and development astd  polaris wins two prestigious awards for its highly innovative core banking and wealth implementations at th asian banker technology implementation awards    polaris enters cloud computing space through strategic investment in identrust   entered into a business purchase agreement with pyxis a specialized player in front office and market risk related to cash and derivatives instruments subsidiariesedit apart from the polaris financial technology limited’s global subsidiaries the company has the following subsidiaries and associate companies polaris enterprise solutions limited pesl  a  subsidiary of polaris financial technology incorporated in india is a leading technology provider in retail manufacturing logistics  distribution telecom  media and travel industry nms works software private limited nms  nms is primarily engaged in the business of designing network management in telecommunication and internet services sonali polaris ft limited  polaris ft has entered into a jv agreement with sonali bank to implement online real time core banking solution for sonali bank and bangladesh commerce bank and offer services to other banks and financial institutions in bangladesh accordingly the company has incorporated a subsidiary company with  holding named sonali polaris ft limited in terms of the jv agreement education and trainingedit nalanda the corporate university of polaris is aimed at bringing the core of organizational processes together through learning and development initiatives that would enable associates to reach out to the latest modules and approaches to organizational learning polaris school of financial technology soft aims creating skilled associates to service its premier clients it will offer certificate courses at both the ‘primer’ and ‘practitioner’ levels executive fasttrack modules in retail banking core banking investment banking and corporate banking as well as customized enterprise training workshops the facility is located in hyderabad recognitionedit  polaris featured in fintech top  companies worldwide providing services to the financial sector at a rank of worldwide  polaris ullas trust wins the best csr practice awards presented by bsenasscomtimes foundation –   recognized as global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia  polaris intellect treasury won the banker capital markets projects award  rated amongst forbes world’s best small companies –  controversiesedit in december  the chairman of the company arun jain and sr vice president rajiv malhotra were detained by indonesian police over commercial dispute with a local bank artha graha on fraud charges jain and malhotra were released by the police after major diplomatic intervention by indian government in october  market regulator sebi barred polaris software labss cmd arun jain from securities market for a period of two years for insider trading in the companys shares sebi had charged him with trading in the stock on the basis of unpublished price sensitive information relating to a proposed acquisition by the firm sebi found that polaris software lab had called off the proposed acquisition of data inc after due diligence in the second week of september  but had informed the concerned stock exchanges on september   jain dealt in  shares of the company on behalf of polaris holding private ltd phpl on the basis of unpublished price sensitive information held by him and had made unfair gains to the tune of rs  lakh during the relevant time phpl was one of the promoters entity of polaris software labs and jain was one of the directors of phpl however in november  madras high court today stayed a sebi order which had barred polaris financial technology cmd arun jain from operating in securities market for a period of two years for alleged insider trading in the companys shares referencesedit  polaris consulting and services limited  head office   httpwwwmoneycontrolcomstocksstockmarketcorpnoticesphpautono  httpwwwmoneycontrolcomstocksstockmarketcorpnoticesphpautono  virtusapolaris in tune to achieve target of synergy revenue of  mn   httpwwwpolarisftcomaboutusaboutusasp  about aesys   financial technology ltd polaris company zxzxxzannouncements   citigroup partner   financial technology ltd polaris company announcements   httpeconomictimesindiatimescomtechitesvirtusapolarislaunchnewbrandidentityarticleshowcms  polaris launches ft   the worlds first design center for financial technology   polaris software lab ltd   citi bank   sei cmm level    ullas trust   polestar trust   wholly owned subsidiary founded in uk   sei cmm level    iso  certified   polaris retail infotech   initial public offering   best international business excellence   cmmi level    top  best small companies   merged with orbitech   intellect   optimus   the banker technology award   superspecialty center for financial risk management   intellect suite   ranked th by nasscom   mother teresa corporate citizen award   softwarelabltdtickerpolarissoftmajorsector super specialty center for investment banking check url value help   belfast   entry into latin america   global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia   pace lab   specialty application development  nd year in a row   nearshore testing center inaugurated in canada   polaris acquired seec   best csr practice awards   polaris acquired laser soft   laser soft won ndtv business leadership awards   polaris acquired indigotx   launched intellect privacy internet banking security card   launched intellect™ gub m    early technology adopter   polaris launches the school of financial technology   f