officesedit polaris is headquartered in chennai and has offices around the world in april  polaris launched its  ft design center  the worlds first center dedicated to financial technology  ft design center is spread over  sq ft and is located in the  acre polaris campus on the it highway in chennai milestonesedit  polaris software lab ltd incorporated   endtoend retail banking solution for citi bank india   quality processes aligned to sei cmm level    operations set up in usa  ullas trust – polaris’ csr was formed   first overseas development centre commissioned for citi bankcitation needed  wholly owned subsidiary founded in singapore and usacitation needed  polestar trust instituted to recognize excellence in business and it journalism   polaris awarded most innovative company  wholly owned subsidiary founded in uk   quality processes aligned to sei cmm level    quality processes iso  certified   birth of polaris retail infotech limited   initial public offering oversubscribed by  times   awarded best international business excellence award   became world’s first cmmi level  company   nasscom felicitated polaris software  ranked amongst top  best small companies in the world for the nd time   historic merger with orbitech citigroup subsidiary  birth of intellect   birth of optimus   the banker technology award   superspecialty center for financial risk management inaugurated in mumbai   launch of intellect suite of products for banking solutions   ranked th by nasscom top  exporters   received mother teresa corporate citizen award   world’s first super specialty center for investment banking the capital inaugurated in hyderabad   near shore centre inaugurated in belfast   entry into latin america   recognized as global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia   launched pace lab in sydney   won global leader in the specialty application development  nd year in a row   nearshore testing center inaugurated in canada   acquired seec inc the worldwide soa based insurance solution provider  polaris ullas trust won the best csr practice awards presented by bsenasscomtimes foundation  acquired laser soft info systems limited a leading banking software products company  laser soft won ndtv business leadership awards  under the ‘inclusion and diversity’ category  indigotx a saas company that provides go tx brokerage platform  launched intellect privacy internet banking security card an online and internet banking security card   launched intellect™ gub m  the most comprehensive enterprise banking solution   intellect wins the “early technology adopter” award at acord loma forum   polaris launches the school of financial technology   sampada a polarislaser soft initiative was awarded the best csr practice award at the th bse social and corporate governance awards jury meet held in mumbai  polaris makes strategic investment in identrust a global leader in trusted identity solutions  polaris was certified as ‘champion of learning’ by the american society of training and development astd  polaris wins two prestigious awards for its highly innovative core banking and wealth implementations at th asian banker technology implementation awards    polaris enters cloud computing space through strategic investment in identrust   entered into a business purchase agreement with pyxis a specialized player in front office and market risk related to cash and derivatives instruments subsidiariesedit apart from the polaris financial technology limited’s global subsidiaries the company has the following subsidiaries and associate companies polaris enterprise solutions limited pesl  a  subsidiary of polaris financial technology incorporated in india is a leading technology provider in retail manufacturing logistics  distribution telecom  media and travel industry nms works software private limited nms  nms is primarily engaged in the business of designing network management in telecommunication and internet services sonali polaris ft limited  polaris ft has entered into a jv agreement with sonali bank to implement online real time core banking solution for sonali bank and bangladesh commerce bank and offer services to other banks and financial institutions in bangladesh accordingly the company has incorporated a subsidiary company with  holding named sonali polaris ft limited in terms of the jv agreement education and trainingedit nalanda the corporate university of polaris is aimed at bringing the core of organizational processes together through learning and development initiatives that would enable associates to reach out to the latest modules and approaches to organizational learning polaris school of financial technology soft aims creating skilled associates to service its premier clients it will offer certificate courses at both the ‘primer’ and ‘practitioner’ levels executive fasttrack modules in retail banking core banking investment banking and corporate banking as well as customized enterprise training workshops the facility is located in hyderabad recognitionedit  polaris featured in fintech top  companies worldwide providing services to the financial sector at a rank of worldwide  polaris ullas trust wins the best csr practice awards presented by bsenasscomtimes foundation –   recognized as global leader in the specialty application development by cybermedia  polaris intellect treasury won the banker capital markets projects award  rated amongst forbes world’s best small companies –  controversiesedit in december  the chairman of the company arun jain and sr vice president rajiv malhotra were detained by indonesian police over commercial dispute with a local bank artha graha on fraud charges jain and malhotra were released by the police after major diplomatic intervention by indian government in october  market regulator sebi barred polaris software labss cmd arun jain from securities market for a period of two years for insider trading in the companys shares sebi had charged him